slip 7
Que.1. Write a menu driven program to perform the following stack and queue related

operations: [Hint: use Array_push(), Array_pop(), Array_shift(), Array_unshift() ]

a) Insert an element in stack

b) Delete an element from stack

c) Display the contents of stack

d) Insert an element in queue

e) Delete an element from queue

f) Display the contents of queue


<?php
$stack = array();
$queue = array();

while(true) {
    echo "\n------ MENU ------\n";
    echo "1. Insert element in STACK\n";
    echo "2. Delete element from STACK\n";
    echo "3. Display STACK\n";
    echo "4. Insert element in QUEUE\n";
    echo "5. Delete element from QUEUE\n";
    echo "6. Display QUEUE\n";
    echo "7. Exit\n";
    echo "Enter your choice: ";
    
    $choice = intval(trim(fgets(STDIN)));

    switch($choice) {
        case 1:
            echo "Enter element to insert in STACK: ";
            $ele = trim(fgets(STDIN));
            array_push($stack, $ele);   // Stack push
            echo "Element inserted in STACK.\n";
            break;

        case 2:
            if(empty($stack)) {
                echo "STACK is empty.\n";
            } else {
                $deleted = array_pop($stack);  // Stack pop
                echo "Deleted element from STACK: $deleted\n";
            }
            break;

        case 3:
            if(empty($stack)) {
                echo "STACK is empty.\n";
            } else {
                echo "STACK contents: ";
                print_r($stack);
            }
            break;

        case 4:
            echo "Enter element to insert in QUEUE: ";
            $ele = trim(fgets(STDIN));
            array_push($queue, $ele);   // Queue insert at end
            echo "Element inserted in QUEUE.\n";
            break;

        case 5:
            if(empty($queue)) {
                echo "QUEUE is empty.\n";
            } else {
                $deleted = array_shift($queue);  // Queue remove from front
                echo "Deleted element from QUEUE: $deleted\n";
            }
            break;

        case 6:
            if(empty($queue)) {
                echo "QUEUE is empty.\n";
            } else {
                echo "QUEUE contents: ";
                print_r($queue);
            }
            break;

        case 7:
            echo "Exiting program. Thank you!\n";
            exit();

        default:
            echo "Invalid choice! Please try again.\n";
    }
}
?>


Q2. Write a program in python to perform following task

[15 Marks]

1. Import Dataset and do the followings:

a) Describing the dataset

b) b) Shape of the dataset

c) c)Display first 3rows from dataset

2. Data.csv has two categorical columns (the country column, and the purchased

column)


import pandas as pd

# 1. Import Dataset
data = pd.read_csv("Data.csv")  # Make sure Data.csv is in the same folder

# 1(a) Describing the dataset
print("----- Describing the Dataset -----")
print(data.describe(include='all'))  # include='all' to include categorical columns

# 1(b) Shape of the dataset
print("\n----- Shape of the Dataset -----")
print("Rows, Columns =", data.shape)

# 1(c) Display first 3 rows
print("\n----- First 3 Rows -----")
print(data.head(3))

# 2. Identify categorical columns
print("\n----- Categorical Columns -----")
print("The dataset has two categorical columns: 'Country' and 'Purchased'")
print(data[['Country', 'Purchased']].head())
